In the second place, while those whose choice is unhampered from the start will deliberate on that other question, whether they wish to pass their lives in obscurity, in your case there is not a free choice. Your ability and energy have thrust you into the work of the world 3 so have the charm of your writings and the friendships you have made Ἰ with famous and notable men.
